This project simulates behavior of 2 bodies under force of the gravity

To build this project cmake is required. Open project folder in terminal, then create folder build. Then write "cmake -B "build"", and "cmake --build".

To run the project just open build folder and find the executable.

To edit the parameters you need to pause simulation(button pause), enter digits in the file “num_enter.txt” in the lines “x1,y1,…”, save the file and press the button “refresh", that corresponds the parameter you have changed.
